## Summary
Amplitude Data's tracking plan feature allows teams to define, document, and manage events, properties, and sources in a centralized location. The article explains how to create and update tracking plans, including creating events with metadata, defining properties with data types and rules, establishing sources for data origin, and collaborating with team members before implementation.

